cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper focuses on deploying deep learning models on smartphones for efficient perceptual image enhancement. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions measuring runtime and memory requirements, which suggests a possible fit for cs.MM (Multimedia). The use of deep learning models also suggests a possible fit for cs.LG (Machine Learning), and the focus on real-world photo enhancement suggests a possible fit for cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper mentions a user study, which suggests a possible fit for cs.GR (Graphics).
